@baseUrl = http://localhost:8004

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Store Simple Test Document (1536-dim)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/store
Content-Type: application/json

### Ingest Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "text": "Machine learning is a subset of artificial intelligence that enables systems to learn and improve from experience.",
    "metadata": {
      "source": "knowledge_base",
      "category": "AI"
    }
  }
]

### LLM Chat Completion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/chat/completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful AI assistant specializing in technology."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is machine learning?"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 512
}

### Find Similar Exceptions with LLM Explanations (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/similar-exceptions/EXC-2024-001?limit=3

### Find Similar Exceptions without LLM Explanations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/similar-exceptions/EXC-2024-001?limit=3&explain=false

### Find More Similar Exceptions (5 results with explanations)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/similar-exceptions/EXC-2024-001?limit=5&explain=true

### Ingest Exception Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rag/documents/ingest-exception
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trade_id": "TRD-2024-001",
  "exception_id": "EXC-2024-001"
}